    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just what people say to be nice. the truth is some things just can't be managed. i've seen people try for years and they just end up more exhausted and miserable. sometimes it feels like the most honest thing to do is just accept that the damage is done and stop fighting a losing battle. don't you think there's a point where just constantly struggling is more harmful than just... letting go?",
